room_title: Escape room "Western Whistle" by Key To Escape in Nashua
room_description: You are about to complete your doctoral program under a forward-thinking professor. You and your team are invited along for a ride, back to 1880 with Dr. Odd. Upon arriving at The Western Whistle, a pioneering western saloon, Dr. Odd informs you of the true nature of the visit. Dr. Odd is testing your team to see if you are truly worthy of the program. Can you solve Dr. Oddâ€™s puzzles in time to hitch a ride back to today?
